 er questions.\n \n\nConcepts Covered: Coworking\, Getting Help\, Making Pr
 ogress\, Crossing Things Off the To-Do list\n \n\nSpeaker: Community\n \n\
 nPrerequisites: No prior experience is required.\n \n\nSoftware Required: 
 Bring what you need.\n \n\nPlease RSVP.
LOCATION:DataLab Classroom\, 360 Shields Library
